replies.body:
Thank you so much for replying and explaining this for me, and any others who read it. Do you know roughly how long it takes now to progress within the honour system? [Of course it's different for everyone, depending on how 'honourable' you are, how many honours you receive, whether they be from premades or strangers and how often you play], I know that at one point it was really quite slow and that a few months ago in the patch notes it was mentioned that they had applied a fix to honour level progression, just that they never really elaborated on exactly what the changes were, beyond that.

If anyone knows I'd be grateful for the info. n_n

{{sticker:sg-miss-fortune}}
